We recommended that Management:

Create the Inventory Committee of the LGU and exert extra effort to conduct complete physical count of all PPE; prepare the RPCPPE; and reconcile the report with the accounting records;

Instruct the Municipal Treasurer to prepare the inventory of the remaining unserviceable properties, if any, based on the RPCPPE for appropriate action; and prepare and/or renew the Acknowledgement Receipt of Equipment (ARE) to the actual holder of the PPE items.

